      <title>汤姆·福特以 8000 万英镑购入伦敦豪宅，创今年最高成交价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/tom-ford-buys-80-million-london-mansion-in-year-s-top-uk-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国亿万富翁汤姆·福特以超过 8000 万英镑（1.04 亿美元）的价格购买了伦敦高档切尔西区的一栋豪宅，这是英国今年最昂贵的住宅交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/tom-ford-buys-80-million-london-mansion-in-year-s-top-uk-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
